{"tid":839624,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"AV界「暗黑郭雪芙」自爆將引退　男粉絲心碎喊別走","createTime":"2018-09-28T05:33:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-28T15:26:03.000Z","uid":32511,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"28cd689f6017705b431724698b69fe7e4c95ef7c","tid":839624,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T05:33:39.000Z","msg":"日本AV女優鈴村愛里(鈴村あいり)有著魔鬼般的火辣D奶身材，加上乾淨又白皙的肌膚和<br />\n一頭短髮，造型和輪廓神似藝人郭雪芙，在AV界有「暗黑郭雪芙」的稱號，擄獲了不少男<br />\n粉絲的心。<br />\n <br />\n鈴村愛里時常會在推特上與粉絲分享日常生活中的趣事，但今(26)日凌晨她卻突然在推特<br />\n上連續發表多則動態，宣告自己即將引退，讓不少男粉絲哭哭心碎。<br />\n <br />\n她在推特上寫道「去年の今頃を考えたら、どんな幕引きであっても皆さんにさようなら<br />\nが言えるだけマシなんですよね（回想起去年的這時，不管引退形式是什麼，光是能挺起<br />\n胸膛和各位說再見，就算是價值連城了）。」不過最後她也提到，自己總是抱持著無論何<br />\n時結束，都能坦然接受的心態去面對這份工作。<br />\n <br />\n今年6月鈴村愛里才剛舉辦粉絲感謝祭，2天1夜不含啪啪啪的溫泉旅遊行程，每人要價14<br />\n萬6000日圓(約4萬台幣)，即使要價不斐，一推出名額還是立馬被粉絲秒殺，這次凌晨突<br />\n然預告引退的消息，不只男粉絲心碎，也讓不少網友質疑鈴村愛里此時宣布引退，可能與<br />\n最近日本AV界多位大咖女優的無碼片段被惡意流出有關。"},{"pid":"ffc5f55d0dc86593a5263d6396ba4e7a2475697f","tid":839624,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T05:41:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92444157940c2be06f2ea706b74e7d595d28ca19","tid":839624,"uid":136186,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T05:42:27.000Z","msg":"不含啪啪啪去黎做乜"},{"pid":"e0394f4996a92ca38c09dfe5fb746ea5870eb483","tid":839624,"uid":294,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T05:47:44.000Z","msg":"暗黑郭芙"},{"pid":"a2deb050686a7f5309d677c7511eea899d6d2c5f","tid":839624,"uid":67208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T05:58:19.000Z","msg":"好在唔係 鈴村いろは"},{"pid":"ce76d2bf6956495194d83c2b88fd25fdbceb7ce1","tid":839624,"uid":137569,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T05:58:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/28/135737_f1d7f1d6fc0e6ebf68c7bc2ce5b404ee.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F28%2F135737_f1d7f1d6fc0e6ebf68c7bc2ce5b404ee.png&h=9b5f36dd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/28/135740_40fe56ed64f028f89bde2af62125cac0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F28%2F135740_40fe56ed64f028f89bde2af62125cac0.png&h=037a2e96&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/28/135742_45976a05c8b818e3780c81aeb740c1e6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F28%2F135742_45976a05c8b818e3780c81aeb740c1e6.png&h=8ee90669&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n補張圖都唔補，懶撚過閪<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55be3c7dd5b3fad155c57c8a8f6f01123919cccb","tid":839624,"uid":57170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"92444157940c2be06f2ea706b74e7d595d28ca19","tid":839624,"uid":136186,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T05:42:27.000Z","msg":"不含啪啪啪去黎做乜"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T15:24:17.000Z","msg":"冇本番都重有大把野玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5e552ef9aeb1a5ca0af45f0c3d5adcf451a6a4a","tid":839624,"uid":48169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T15:26:03.000Z","msg":"D?"}]}